SELECT DISTINCT pogId
,ag.subOrderId
,ag.orderDate
,atb.Channel
,atb.utmContent
FROM `temp.attributedOrders_1` atb
LEFT JOIN
(
SELECT DISTINCT pogId
,subOrderId
,TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000)) AS orderDate
FROM `all(agCmDump)`
WHERE DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000))) BETWEEN 1 AND 7
) ag
ON ag.subOrderId = atb.subOrderId
","temp.pog_ord_L7days")

run(sql="

SELECT CASE WHEN NM3SO <= 10 THEN '1_LT10'
            WHEN NM3SO > 10 AND NM3SO <= 15 THEN '2_Bw10and15'
            WHEN NM3SO > 15 AND NM3SO <= 20 THEN '3_Bw15and20'
            WHEN NM3SO > 20 AND NM3SO <= 30 THEN '4_Bw20and30'
            WHEN NM3SO > 30 THEN '5_GT30'
            ELSE NM3SO END AS nm
        ,availability
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%cpt1%' THEN 'cpt1'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS cpt1
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%sale%' THEN 'sale'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS sale
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%mroas%' THEN 'mroas'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS mroas
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%acpt%' THEN 'acpt'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS acpt 
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%mcpt%' THEN 'mcpt'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS mcpt
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT f.dmPublisherInfoId) AS pogs
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT t.subOrderId)   AS sdSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' THEN t.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)  AS fbSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%fb%' AND LOWER(t.utmContent) LIKE '%cpt%' THEN t.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)  AS fbCPTSubo
        
        ,SUM(NM3SO) AS NM3
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT orderDate) AS days

FROM `temp.FB_Live_New_Feed` f
JOIN `temp.nmso_final` p
ON f.dmPublisherInfoId = p.pogId

LEFT JOIN `temp.pog_ord_L7days` t
ON f.dmPublisherInfoId = t.pogId

GROUP BY availability
        ,CASE WHEN NM3SO <= 10 THEN '1_LT10'
            WHEN NM3SO > 10 AND NM3SO <= 15 THEN '2_Bw10and15'
            WHEN NM3SO > 15 AND NM3SO <= 20 THEN '3_Bw15and20'
            WHEN NM3SO > 20 AND NM3SO <= 30 THEN '4_Bw20and30'
            WHEN NM3SO > 30 THEN '5_GT30'
            ELSE NM3SO END 
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%cpt1%' THEN 'cpt1'
                ELSE 'Others' END 
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%sale%' THEN 'sale'
                ELSE 'Others' END 
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%mroas%' THEN 'mroas'
                ELSE 'Others' END 
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%acpt%' THEN 'acpt'
                ELSE 'Others' END 
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%mcpt%' THEN 'mcpt'
                ELSE 'Others' END 

ORDER BY nm, availability    
",1000)

run("

SELECT CASE WHEN BAU_NM3_FEED <= 12 THEN '1_LT12'
            WHEN BAU_NM3_FEED > 12 AND BAU_NM3_FEED <= 25 THEN '2_Bw12and25'
            WHEN BAU_NM3_FEED > 25 THEN '3_GT25'
            ELSE BAU_NM3_FEED END AS nm
        ,availability
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%cpt1%' THEN 'cpt1'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS cpt1
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%sale%' THEN 'sale'
                ELSE 'Others' END AS sale
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT f.dmPublisherInfoId) AS pogs
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT t.subOrderId)   AS sdSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%facebook%' THEN t.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)  AS fbSubo
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LOWER(Channel) LIKE '%facebook%' AND LOWER(t.utmContent) LIKE '%cpt%' THEN t.subOrderId ELSE NULL END)  AS fbCPTSubo
        
        ,SUM(BAU_NM3_FEED) AS NM3
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT orderDate) AS days

FROM `temp.FB_Live_New_Feed` f
JOIN `temp.nm` p
ON f.dmPublisherInfoId = p.POG

LEFT JOIN `temp.pog_ord_L7days` t
ON f.dmPublisherInfoId = t.pogId

GROUP BY availability
        ,CASE WHEN BAU_NM3_FEED <= 12 THEN '1_LT12'
            WHEN BAU_NM3_FEED > 12 AND BAU_NM3_FEED <= 25 THEN '2_Bw12and25'
            WHEN BAU_NM3_FEED > 25 THEN '3_GT25'
            ELSE BAU_NM3_FEED END
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%cpt1%' THEN 'cpt1'
                ELSE 'Others' END
        ,CASE WHEN LOWER(customLabel2) LIKE '%sale%' THEN 'sale'
                ELSE 'Others' END

ORDER BY nm, availability    
",1000)
